lee much more mobile.   This potion is very easy to make once you get your pottery to about 120 (min 122), and about 300pp should accomplish this as pottery is one of the cheapest skills to build.  The components are very common drops in Velks.  One trip to Velks should get you enough components for several potions.  The cool thing is, you can have most of the potion put together in the bank, so when you gate to Thurg, you simple go to the bank, and visit a merchant very close by and make another (5 min max), the head to the book and be on your way.<br>
<br>
